Before starting this game, you must have the AMOS.library in LIBS:


The purpose of this game is to shoot a target, which is moving on a
carpet. All the target are not moving at the same speed. The score
when you hit a target is proportional to the speed and accuracy of the
shoot.
To shoot if you play alone, use the left button of your mouse. If you
play at 2, the first player use the button of the joystick, and the
second, the button of the mouse.

This game has been done with AmosPro. But now Blitz rules !

